A Lesotho national domestic worker told the police that she was cleaning the house when she heard the door open. As she approached the staircase she saw two males, who covered her face and locked her into one of the bedrooms. Middelburg Police spokesperson, Captain Khanyisile Zwane, said the robbers made off with an X-box, television set and a cellphone. No injuries were sustained, the police are yet to make an arrest. â€¢ A house robbery case was opened with the Middelburg Police.